SELECT SUM(amount) AS total_expenses FROM Expenses WHERE date_incurred BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-06-30';

SELECT budget_name, total_amount, COUNT(*) AS expense_count FROM Budgets JOIN Expenses ON Budgets.id = Expenses.budget_id GROUP BY budget_name, total_amount HAVING expense_count > 5 ORDER BY total_amount DESC;

SELECT category_id, category_name FROM budget_categories WHERE category_id > 5;
SELECT * FROM budget_transactions WHERE amount > 1000 ORDER BY transaction_date DESC, category ASC;

SELECT category_name, SUM(amount) AS total_amount FROM budget_transactions JOIN budget_categories ON budget_transactions.category = budget_categories.category_name GROUP BY category_name HAVING total_amount > 5000;
SELECT user_id, username, email FROM budget_users WHERE username LIKE '%admin%' ORDER BY user_id ASC;
SELECT * FROM budget_transactions WHERE amount <= 500 AND (category = 'Groceries' OR category = 'Restaurants') ORDER BY transaction_date DESC;

SELECT t.transaction_id, t.transaction_date, t.amount, c.category_name FROM budget_transactions t JOIN budget_categories c ON t.category = c.category_name WHERE t.amount > 500 AND c.category_id IN (2, 4) ORDER BY t.transaction_date ASC, c.category_name DESC;
